<p><i><b>Special People</b></i> is a 2007 British film was directed by <a href="/wiki/Justin_Edgar" title="Justin Edgar">Justin Edgar</a> for <a href="/wiki/104_Films" title="104 Films">104 Films</a>. The film received widespread press coverage as a result of censorship of its disability themes.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>
</p>
